messages.content: Investigate the log and then answer this. How many calls happenned in this log? Can you provider their call id, their start time, their end time, and how many participants were in them?

I found six distinct calls in the log.  
For every call I took  

• the first time-stamp where the callId appears as the start time  
• the last “ExtendedCallState … 6 ⇒ 7” (or equivalent final state) entry as the end time  
• the number of “participant added for call <callId> …” lines as a quick way to gauge how many other people actually joined that call (duplicates removed).
